    link: 'https://blog.aidxn.com/posts/website-pageload-optimisation/',
  },
  {
    name: 'Case Study: Competing in competitive niches.',
    desc: 'We generated amazing results for a client by optimising Google ad campaigns to target their customer with informative creatives.',
